OL,3,CMore than #13bn promised for infected
OL,4,Cblood and Horizon scandal victims
OL,6,FRachel Reeves made the announcement at
OL,7,Fthe start of the Budget
OL,9,FThe chancellor has announced the
OL,10,Fgovernment is setting aside more than
OL,11,F#13 billion to pay compensation to the
OL,12,Fvictims of the infected blood and
OL,13,FHorizon scandals.
OL,15,FRachel Reeves made the announcement at
OL,16,Fthe start of the first Labour Budget
OL,17,Fin almost 15 years, promising to set
OL,18,Faside #11.8bn for the victims of the
OL,19,Finfected blood scandal with #1.8bn for
OL,20,Fthe subpostmasters who were wrongly
OL,21,Fconvicted by the Post Office.
