OL,3,CMore than #13bn promised for infected
OL,4,Cblood and Horizon scandal victims
OL,6,FDuring the announcement, the
OL,7,Fchancellor accused the Conservatives
OL,8,Fof not setting aside any money to pay
OL,9,Ffor the compensation saying: "The
OL,10,FLeader of the Opposition rightly made
OL,11,Fan unequivocal apology for the
OL,12,Finjustice of the infected blood
OL,13,Fscandal on behalf of the British
OL,14,Fstate... but he did not budget for the
OL,15,Fcosts of compensation."
OL,17,FShe said the announcement is "long
OL,18,Foverdue for the pain and injustice
OL,19,Fthat they have suffered."
