OL,3,CMore than #13bn promised for infected
OL,4,Cblood and Horizon scandal victims
OL,6,FThe handling of the compensation
OL,7,Fschemes for both scandals has been
OL,8,Fcriticised by victims and campaigners
OL,9,Ffor taking too long.
OL,11,FPost Office CEO Nick Read told the
OL,12,FHorizon Inquiry earlier this month he
OL,13,Ffelt "deep regret" over how the
OL,14,Fcompensation had been handled.
OL,16,FEarlier this week ITV News reported
OL,17,FParliament would launch an inquiry
OL,18,Finto the delays in providing the
OL,19,Fcompensation to subpostmasters.
