OL,3,CMore than #13bn promised for infected
OL,4,Cblood and Horizon scandal victims
OL,6,FBetween 1999 and 2015, more than 700
OL,7,FPost Office sub-postmasters were
OL,8,Fconvicted of theft or false accounting
OL,9,Fand thousands more were forced to make
OL,10,Fup shortfalls due to a problem with
OL,11,FFujitsu's Horizon software.
OL,13,FFour suicides were blamed on the
OL,14,Fscandal.
OL,16,FFormer prime minister Rishi Sunak
OL,17,Fcalled it one of the greatest
OL,18,Fmiscarriages of justice in British
OL,19,Fhistory, with Parliament overturning
OL,20,Fall of the convictions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
