OL,3,CMore than #13bn promised for infected
OL,4,Cblood and Horizon scandal victims
OL,6,FIn total, more than 3,000 people are
OL,7,Fknown to have died.
OL,9,FMany of those who were infected had to
OL,10,Fgive up their jobs and live on
OL,11,Fbenefits because of health problems
OL,12,Fand many of these are now entitled to
OL,13,Fcompensation.
OL,15,FThe average package is expected to be
OL,16,Faround #100,000 but some are set to
OL,17,Freceive much more.
